data.description: *Multiple offers received, highest and best due Wednesday, 4/10 @ 9am* Charming Cape Cod in Fountain Hill offering 3 bedrooms & 1.5 bathrooms! Upon entering, you're greeted with a spacious living room with hardwood floor and brick faced fireplace. Through the arched doorway is the open concept kitchen with SS appliances, white cabinetry, adjacent dining room, half bath, and access to the backyard. Upstairs are all three bedrooms and a full bathroom. The basement includes the laundry room and extra storage space. Outside is a covered patio opening to a nicely sized yard perfect for entertaining. Showings start at the open house this Saturday, 4/6 from 1pm- 3pm!
